overview:
TemplateMela is a leading website template provider company, which helps software companies, web companies and other internet business owners in transforming the look of their website.

TemplateMela offers a vast collection of fresh and appealing ecommerce templates of premium quality. They offer Ecommerce templates, magento templates, prestashop themes, Opencart Templates and joomla templates . Their web templates and themes are developed by their team of creative designers and professional programmers.

The templates available at their website offer incomparable innovative design coupled with functionality and user-friendly interface.
